00:34:35.560 --> 00:34:36.679
At our, uh... whatever that saying is.

00:34:36.719 --> 00:34:37.199
Right?

00:34:37.199 --> 00:34:37.560
Right.

00:34:41.639 --> 00:34:42.080
Brother Ping.

00:34:43.600 --> 00:34:44.520
I'm not lecturing you,

00:34:44.840 --> 00:34:45.840
But if it were me,

00:34:45.920 --> 00:34:46.520
The moment I got out,

00:34:46.520 --> 00:34:47.880
I'd go get revenge on them.

00:34:48.239 --> 00:34:49.320
Think about those two years.

00:34:49.360 --> 00:34:50.040
What did you eat?

00:34:50.040 --> 00:34:50.840
What did you drink?

00:34:51.639 --> 00:34:52.360
And Xing Wu?

00:34:52.719 --> 00:34:53.320
Now,

00:34:53.400 --> 00:34:54.639
He's taken over

00:34:54.639 --> 00:34:55.360
Mr. Ye's electronics mall.

00:34:56.120 --> 00:34:57.640
He's even trying for college now.

00:34:57.720 --> 00:34:58.920
If he gets into college,

00:34:59.320 --> 00:35:00.520
Will he still take us seriously?

00:35:02.720 --> 00:35:03.640
What he does has nothing to do with me.

00:35:04.400 --> 00:35:05.640
I came out to be a decent man.

00:35:07.720 --> 00:35:08.560
Brother Ping, didn't you

00:35:08.720 --> 00:35:09.640
Ask me to look after your sister?

00:35:10.040 --> 00:35:12.520
But Xing Wu's cousin

00:35:13.560 --> 00:35:14.720
Doesn't get along with your sister.

00:35:16.280 --> 00:35:17.120
They're at the same school.

00:35:28.400 --> 00:35:28.760
Serve.

00:35:38.520 --> 00:35:39.320
Why isn't Wu here yet?

00:35:40.000 --> 00:35:41.120
Maybe he overslept.

00:35:41.280 --> 00:35:42.520
He's always on time.

00:35:45.560 --> 00:35:46.600
Get it. Go get the ball. Hurry.

00:35:46.800 --> 00:35:47.560
Consider it a warm-up.

00:35:49.880 --> 00:35:50.400
Wu.

00:35:50.600 --> 00:35:50.960
Wu.

00:35:50.960 --> 00:35:51.640
Why are you so late?

00:35:52.080 --> 00:35:53.400
Are you two waiting for me to play

00:35:53.400 --> 00:35:54.320
Or to fix my bike?

00:35:54.680 --> 00:35:55.280
What do you mean?

00:36:02.440 --> 00:36:04.080
Who took my wheel off?

00:36:06.520 --> 00:36:08.600
Come out and fight me one-on-one.

00:36:09.120 --> 00:36:09.520
I...

00:36:10.320 --> 00:36:11.800
I can't believe this.

00:36:12.880 --> 00:36:13.760
Where's your decency?

00:36:32.600 --> 00:36:33.240
Xing Wu.

00:36:33.560 --> 00:36:34.000
Come on.

00:36:38.600 --> 00:36:40.480
What time is it already?

00:36:40.760 --> 00:36:41.960
Why are there still no customers?

00:36:42.520 --> 00:36:42.960
Lanfang.

00:36:43.120 --> 00:36:44.440
It happens. Some days are slow.

00:36:44.520 --> 00:36:45.520
It's been slow too many times.

00:36:47.760 --> 00:36:48.520
Here comes a customer.

00:36:48.560 --> 00:36:49.280
Haircut?

00:36:49.640 --> 00:36:50.560
Welcome.

00:36:54.720 --> 00:36:55.440
Stop right there.

00:36:56.520 --> 00:36:57.440
Liu Nian.

00:37:00.520 --> 00:37:02.320
Fit it in, then tighten it.

00:37:02.440 --> 00:37:03.440
I did fit it in.

00:37:03.440 --> 00:37:04.720
If it's fitted, what about the brake?

00:37:04.800 --> 00:37:05.320
The brake is sticking out.

00:37:05.320 --> 00:37:05.720
You do it.

00:37:06.200 --> 00:37:07.960
Fine, I'll do it.

00:37:09.280 --> 00:37:09.840
Wu.

00:37:10.040 --> 00:37:11.280
Xuan Island's window was smashed.

00:37:15.000 --> 00:37:16.200
Don't open today.

00:37:20.680 --> 00:37:21.040
Come on.

00:37:24.520 --> 00:37:26.120
No, no what?

00:37:34.440 --> 00:37:35.200
Hello, Officer Xu.

00:37:36.720 --> 00:37:37.680
I want to ask about someone.

00:37:38.440 --> 00:37:38.840
Go ahead.

00:37:40.440 --> 00:37:41.000
Cao Ping.

00:37:42.400 --> 00:37:43.360
Has he been released from prison?

00:37:44.280 --> 00:37:44.640
Yes.

00:37:45.280 --> 00:37:46.360
Just a few days ago.

00:37:46.920 --> 00:37:48.040
He even came to the station

00:37:48.080 --> 00:37:49.600
To register and report in.

00:37:52.040 --> 00:37:52.520
Xing Wu.

00:37:53.240 --> 00:37:53.640
Xing Wu.

00:37:55.040 --> 00:37:56.000
Did something happen?

00:37:56.400 --> 00:37:56.880
I see.

00:37:57.720 --> 00:37:58.120
Thank you.

00:38:10.320 --> 00:38:10.880
Where are you?

00:38:20.880 --> 00:38:22.360
Let's see where you can run this time.

00:38:22.520 --> 00:38:23.640
Who are you? What are you doing?

00:38:26.520 --> 00:38:27.120
Xing Wu.

00:38:33.800 --> 00:38:35.160
Xing Wu, who is he?

00:38:36.320 --> 00:38:37.120
Do you know him?

00:38:37.960 --> 00:38:38.600
No.

00:38:40.320 --> 00:38:40.840
It's fine now.

00:38:42.680 --> 00:38:43.640
Let's go home.

00:38:48.280 --> 00:38:49.320
Let's go. It's fine.

00:39:00.840 --> 00:39:01.320
Screw you.

00:39:02.560 --> 00:39:03.320
Xing Wu.

00:39:04.000 --> 00:39:04.840
Get out here.

00:39:07.080 --> 00:39:07.800
What are you doing?

00:39:07.960 --> 00:39:09.040
What's it to you?

00:39:09.440 --> 00:39:10.000
Get back inside.

00:39:11.720 --> 00:39:12.600
Come out, Xing Wu.

00:39:13.240 --> 00:39:14.720
What's going on?

00:39:18.280 --> 00:39:18.800
Yang Gang.

00:39:19.160 --> 00:39:19.960
We didn't mess with you, did we?

00:39:20.120 --> 00:39:21.280
Why keep coming after Shunyi?

00:39:23.680 --> 00:39:25.520
Because you stole my business.

00:39:26.840 --> 00:39:27.640
I'm telling you,

00:39:28.280 --> 00:39:30.000
This turf is mine.

00:39:30.440 --> 00:39:31.600
Don't say I didn't warn you.

00:39:31.800 --> 00:39:33.080
This isn't the old days.

00:39:33.520 --> 00:39:34.080
Either

00:39:34.800 --> 00:39:35.960
You get lost on your own,

00:39:36.400 --> 00:39:37.640
Or my boys help you.

00:39:39.240 --> 00:39:39.760
Give it back.

00:39:39.760 --> 00:39:41.400
Give what back?

00:39:54.720 --> 00:39:55.400
I...

00:39:57.160 --> 00:39:59.040
Coming here looking for trouble?

00:40:04.800 --> 00:40:05.400
Impressive.

00:40:29.680 --> 00:40:30.200
Wu.

00:40:35.080 --> 00:40:35.640
Calm down.

00:40:35.920 --> 00:40:36.440
Wu.

00:40:37.120 --> 00:40:37.680
Calm down.

00:40:38.840 --> 00:40:39.400
Bro.

00:40:40.520 --> 00:40:41.360
Tell Cao Ping

00:40:42.440 --> 00:40:43.240
I want to see him.

00:40:55.880 --> 00:40:56.600
Welcome.

00:41:02.920 --> 00:41:03.640
You're out.

00:41:09.760 --> 00:41:10.440
What are you doing here?

00:41:14.520 --> 00:41:15.520
I wanted to see you.

00:41:19.960 --> 00:41:20.640
Seen enough?

00:41:20.880 --> 00:41:21.640
Can you leave now?

00:41:32.920 --> 00:41:34.200
How have you been these two years?

00:41:34.320 --> 00:41:35.080
What do you think?

00:41:35.640 --> 00:41:36.720
I think I've been fine.

00:41:38.280 --> 00:41:39.320
At least I had ironing to do.

00:41:44.720 --> 00:41:45.720
Go. Hurry.

00:41:46.320 --> 00:41:47.400
I need to go back and review.

00:41:47.760 --> 00:41:48.560
I have an exam next week.

00:41:58.000 --> 00:41:59.080
Then I'll wait until after your exam

00:41:59.080 --> 00:41:59.880
And come see you again.

00:42:02.440 --> 00:42:03.440
Don't come again.

00:42:03.640 --> 00:42:04.440
I don't want others to know

00:42:04.440 --> 00:42:05.280
About our relationship.

00:42:44.240 --> 00:42:44.720
Hello?

00:42:45.520 --> 00:42:46.160
Hello, Brother Ping.

00:42:47.160 --> 00:42:48.320
Xing Wu wants to meet you.

00:43:06.320 --> 00:43:07.000
Xing Wu.

00:43:07.840 --> 00:43:08.680
Long time no see.

00:43:11.400 --> 00:43:13.000
You must hate me now.

00:43:16.840 --> 00:43:18.040
You think too highly of yourself.

00:43:19.240 --> 00:43:20.400
That matter, to me,

00:43:21.320 --> 00:43:22.360
Was over long ago.

00:43:25.720 --> 00:43:26.680
It's over for you,

00:43:27.520 --> 00:43:28.320
But not for me.

00:43:29.200 --> 00:43:29.840
Cao Ping.

00:43:31.360 --> 00:43:32.120
Look forward.

00:43:32.840 --> 00:43:34.520
Stop holding on to the past.

00:43:37.400 --> 00:43:38.560
From the day I went to prison,

00:43:39.440 --> 00:43:40.840
I actually tried to look forward.

00:43:42.560 --> 00:43:43.120
For the past two years,

00:43:43.120 --> 00:43:44.680
Every day, I worked to turn myself around.

00:43:45.200 --> 00:43:46.320
So I could get out sooner

00:43:46.320 --> 00:43:47.240
And reunite with my sister.

00:43:49.120 --> 00:43:50.200
What exactly do you want?

